  • Method Details

    • message

      @NotNull public static @NotNull net.kyori.adventure.text.Component message(@NotNull @NotNull String level, String msg)
      Creates a formatted message component based on the specified level and message.
      Parameters:
      level - The severity level of the message.
      Accepted values are:
      info - for informational messages
      error - for error messages
      Any other value will be treated as an unknown level.
      msg - The content of the message to be formatted.
      Returns:
      A Component object representing the formatted message.
      Since:
      0.1.0 The returned component includes the WikiCraft prefix and the message with appropriate coloring based on the level. For unknown levels, it returns an unknown severity specified error alongside the message.

    • message

      Creates a formatted message component based on the specified level and message.

      Parameters:

    • throwError

      public static void throwError(Exception error, org.bukkit.command.CommandSender sender)
      Logs an error and sends an error message to the specified command sender. This method combines logging the error and notifying the sender in one call.
      Parameters:
      error - The exception that occurred, used for logging and creating the error message.
      sender - The command sender to receive the error message.
